<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Road_coloring_problem&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Jarkko_Kari" title="Jarkko Kari">Jarkko Kari</a>, "Synchronizing finite automata on Eulerian digraphs", <i><a href="/wiki/Theoretical_Computer_Science" title="Theoretical Computer Science">Theoretical Computer Science</a></i> 295 (2003), 223–232.</li>
<li><a href="/w/index.php?title=G._L._O%27Brien&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="G. L. O'Brien (page does not exist)">G. L. O'Brien</a>, "The road-coloring problem", <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Israel_Journal_of_Mathematics&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Israel Journal of Mathematics (page does not exist)">Israel Journal of Mathematics</a></i>, Vol. 39, 1981.</li>
</ul>
